OL,6,FA new Christmas tree installation
OL,7,Fwhich cost #4,000 has split opinion in
OL,8,FCardigan.
OL,10,FThe tree-shaped structure features
OL,11,Fmetal poles which have lights running
OL,12,Fup and down them.
OL,14,FIt has been placed outside the
OL,15,FCeredigion market town's Grade II-
OL,16,Flisted Victorian Guildhall, which
OL,17,Ffunctions as an art gallery and
OL,18,Fcommunity centre.
