OL,3,CChristmas tree installation that cost
OL,4,C#4,000 splits opinion
OL,6,FThe installation has split opinion,
OL,7,Fwith some claiming it's not worth the
OL,8,Ffee, while others acknowledge the need
OL,9,Fto reduce carbon footprint.
OL,11,FCardigan Town Council said it's part
OL,12,Fof cost-cutting measures which will
OL,13,Fhelp save the authority #1,000 a year
OL,14,Fas the structure can be reused.
OL,16,FThe local town council has also argued
OL,17,Fthat cutting and transporting a tree
OL,18,Fevery year doesn't meet its goals to
OL,19,Freduce its carbon footprint.
