OL,6,F"There is also a pressure on councils
OL,7,Fto consider reducing their carbon
OL,8,Ffootprint and to promote biodiversity
OL,9,Fand we agreed as a council that
OL,10,Fcutting and transporting a live tree
OL,11,Fevery year did not support our aim to
OL,12,Fmeet these guidelines."
